                                        M513.173732 829.943282c-16.70752 0-30.30112 13.5936-30.30112 30.30112 0 16.70752 13.5936 30.30112 30.30112 30.30112s30.299073-13.5936 30.299073-30.30112C543.472805 843.536882 529.881253 829.943282 513.173732 829.943282z
